01:12:21.475 --> 01:12:23.433
Sure I can suspect you!

01:12:23.434 --> 01:12:25.809
You're pretty!
You're so damned pretty!

01:12:26.183 --> 01:12:27.434
You're handsome, too!

01:12:30.975 --> 01:12:33.308
