01:12:53.350 --> 01:12:55.225
That damned greenhouse!

01:12:55.767 --> 01:12:59.933
And driving 3000 km in a month!

01:13:00.850 --> 01:13:02.183
Why bring rubber pants?

01:13:02.684 --> 01:13:05.266
